### âœ… Summary

| Concept | Key Type | Used For | Speed |
|----------|-----------|----------|-------|
| **Symmetric Encryption** | One shared key | Actual data transfer | âš¡ Fast |
| **Asymmetric Encryption** | Public + Private keys | Key exchange, authentication | ğŸ¢ Slower |

